---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Shipping & Delivery — Purrtraits"
  description="Delivery times and costs for Purrtraits framed prints and canvas portraits. Printed and shipped by local production partners in the UK, US, Canada, and Australia."
>
  <section class="legal page">
    <div class="container legal__inner">
      <header class="legal__header">
        <p class="legal__eyebrow">SHIPPING</p>
        <h1 class="legal__title display">Shipping &amp; Delivery</h1>
        <p class="muted legal__updated">Printed locally. Delivered fast.</p>
      </header>

      <article class="legal__body">
        <p>
          Every Purrtraits print is produced on demand by our print partner
          <a href="https://www.gelato.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gelato</a>,
          which runs a network of local production facilities around the
          world. Your order is routed to the facility closest to your
          delivery address — so most prints are made and posted within
          your own country, cutting shipping time and carbon footprint.
        </p>

        <h2 class="legal__h2">Estimated delivery times</h2>
        <p>
          Times below cover the full window from order to doorstep,
          including a 1–2 business day production step.
        </p>
        <table class="shipping-table">
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Country</th><th>Typical delivery</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>UK</td><td>2–5 business days</td></tr>
            <tr><td>US</td><td>2–4 business days</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Canada</td><td>3–6 business days</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Australia</td><td>4–7 business days</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Other countries</td><td>4–7 business days</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <p class="muted shipping__note">
          These are typical ranges, not guarantees. Remote regions and
          peak periods (e.g. December) can add a few days.
        </p>

        <h2 class="legal__h2">Digital downloads</h2>
        <p>
          Digital portraits don't ship — you'll get an instant high-res
          download as soon as your payment clears, and a copy of the link
          by email.
        </p>

        <h2 class="legal__h2">Tracking your order</h2>
        <p>
          Once your print leaves the production facility you'll receive
          a shipping confirmation email with a tracking link. You can
          also see the status of every order in your
          <a href="/gallery">gallery</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="legal__h2">Lost, damaged, or late deliveries</h2>
        <p>
          If your order arrives damaged or hasn't shown up within 10
          business days of the estimated window, email
          <a href="mailto:hello@purrtraits.shop">hello@purrtraits.shop</a>
          with your order number and we'll arrange a replacement or
          refund — no quibbles.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal__inner { max-width: 760px; }
  .legal__header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .legal__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--c-pink);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .legal__title { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .legal__updated { font-size: 14px; }

  .legal__body {
    background: var(--c-white);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--c-stroke-light);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    padding: 28px 22px;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--c-dark);
  }
  .legal__body p { margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .legal__body a { color: var(--c-pink); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }
  .legal__body a:hover { color: #c98399; }

  .legal__h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 26px;
    color: var(--c-dark);
    margin: 28px 0 10px;
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--c-pink-light);
  }

  .shipping-table {
    width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15px;
    margin: 6px 0 6px;
  }
  .shipping-table th {
    text-align: left;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--c-text);
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--c-stroke-light);
  }
  .shipping-table th:last-child { text-align: right; }
  .shipping-table td {
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-stroke-light);
    color: var(--c-dark);
  }
  .shipping-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .shipping-table td:last-child { text-align: right; color: var(--c-text); }

  .shipping__note { font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px; }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .legal__body { padding: 44px 48px; font-size: 16px; }
    .legal__h2 { font-size: 30px; }
    .shipping-table, .shipping-table th, .shipping-table td { font-size: 16px; }
  }
</style>
